WEBVTT

00:00.901 --> 00:02.436
Previously on "The Path"...

00:02.469 --> 00:05.273
I relinquish my guilt
for being with Cal.

00:05.306 --> 00:09.043
Everything else I've done
that is horrible this year...

00:09.077 --> 00:10.044
Uhh!

00:10.078 --> 00:11.612
She chose me!

00:11.645 --> 00:13.681
Just... like...

00:13.714 --> 00:15.083
Steve.

00:15.116 --> 00:17.318
- You're a Denier, Eddie.

00:19.620 --> 00:21.489
Deniers need to stay
where they belong.

00:22.590 --> 00:24.325
- Felicia... were you...

00:24.358 --> 00:26.394
- Richard told me everything.

00:26.427 --> 00:28.362
But I need to hear it from you.

00:28.396 --> 00:30.131
I just need the files

00:30.164 --> 00:33.067
for every disgruntled Meyerist
who has ever left.

00:33.101 --> 00:35.403
- The blackmail victims
that I have lined up for Penetti

00:35.436 --> 00:38.272
are pieces of shit,
but they sent me back in there

00:38.306 --> 00:41.075
because The Movement was
causing trouble for DeKann,

00:41.109 --> 00:43.177
Penetti's biggest
campaign donor.

00:43.211 --> 00:45.179
Eddie, my name isn't Sam.

00:45.213 --> 00:47.615
- Mary, get in the car.

00:49.683 --> 00:51.785
How did you find out
about me and Cal?

00:51.819 --> 00:53.687
- Why don't you tell me

00:53.721 --> 00:56.690
the rest of the horrible things
you've done this past year.

